rows.label: qst201605_msg0001
rows.name: All skills have reached level 2, mo!

rows.label: qst201605_msg0002
rows.name:
Then let's get on stage right
away and have a concert, mo!

rows.label: qst201605_msg0003
rows.name:
What?! I-I can't do something
like that so suddenly!

rows.label: qst201605_msg0004
rows.name: Everyone's a beginner at first, mo!

rows.label: qst201605_msg0005
rows.name:
Experience is the most
important thing, mo!

rows.label: qst201605_msg0007
rows.name:
Leave all the concert
arrangements to Teetapz, mo!

rows.label: qst201605_msg0008
rows.name:
The venue is here, at the
Harapekko Canteen, mo.

rows.label: qst201605_msg0009
rows.name:
Teetapz has a meeting, so
I'll be going ahead, mo.

rows.label: qst201605_msg0010
rows.name:
Nanakoori-san, you should
get ready too, mo.

rows.label: qst201605_msg0011
rows.name: H-How long do I have to get ready?

rows.label: qst201605_msg0013
rows.name:
Everyone else, please come to
the Harapekko Canteen soon, mo.

rows.label: qst201605_msg0016
rows.name:
I have something to discuss,
so please bring her here, mo.
